Authentic Italian Food for Dine In or To Go

Dinner with family and friends never tasted so good. We’re so pleased to be your neighborhood Italian restaurant since 1981! Reserve a table to dine with us by calling your neighborhood Bertucci’s. Want it TO GO? Order online for pasta and pizza delivery or curbside pickup. Planning a gathering for 20 or more? Click GROUP DINING to get all the details you need to plan your special event, family celebration, birthday party, or corporate event. Want the party delivered? Visit our CATERING page for easy ordering.
